<P>
   AUDIO-POP _ Back in 1980, no one would have lumped Lionel Richie
and Linda Ronstadt into the same category. Today these two are
stuck on the same page of the baby-boomer musical yearbook like a
time-warped ``cutest couple.'' On their new albums, neither of
these onetime superstars has changed the formula from the days when
they ruled pop charts. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
