Friday, July 3, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Tina May at (206) 448-8355.
</P>
<P>
   RETROSPECTIVE-JACOB-LAWRENCE (Seattle) ``Intimate''
retrospective on artist Jacob Lawrence, designed to show how his
art reflects his life, opens at the Henry Gallery in Seattle
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   with: INTERVIEW-JACOB-LAWRENCE (Seattle) Interview with the
artist, his current life, his views on the show, biographical
material. PHOTO
</P>
<P>
