<P>
   ECON-NINETIES-REVIEW-NYT _ Suddenly, these are nervous times for
prosperity fans. The stock market has the jitters. The Asian
economic boom, another great engine of American prosperity, is
over. And the nation's economy shows signs of slowing. Is this the
beginning of the end of the Soaring Nineties? By Louis Uchitelle.
