 (ATTENTION: Managing editors, feature editors, health editors)   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service calls your attention to the
following  &UR; health features and columns &LR;  for use this weekend and
beyond.
</P>
<P>
   The stories are from The New York Times (NYT), Boston Globe
(BOS), Cox News Service (COX), Hearst News Service (HNS), Bloomberg
News (BLOOM), Los Angeles Daily News (LADN), Fort Worth
Star-Telegram (TEX), Kansas City Star (KAN) and Arizona Republic
(AZR).
