<P>
   CLINTON-ENVIRONMENT (Guilin, China) _ President Clinton meets
with Chinese environmentalists who warn that environmental concerns
are likely to be traded off against economic considerations in a
nation struggling to overcome poverty. By STEWART M. POWELL.
(Already filed)
