top-seeded Marina Hingis in Wimbledon semifinals. By DALE
ROBERTSON.
</P>
<P>
   BWC-SWOOPES (Houston) _ Houston Comets foward Sheryl Swoopes is
hospitalized after fainting during practice. Swoopes, 27, was taken
to a local hospital where she remained under observation. By The
Houston Chronicle.
</P>
