<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-02 20:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8689 &Cx1f; tta-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ECON-REPORT-ART-550&AMP;A     07-02 1146
