<HEADLINE>
GROSSES FOR `ARMAGEDDON' BELOW EXPECTATIONS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
 
  
BY DAVE McNARY  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
