<P>
   CONGRESS/Patients' rights bills -- tk --
(BC-CONGRESS-HEALTHCARE-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO/Locator map -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- (BC-MEXICO-JUAREZ-NYT)
</P>
